    "The code generated could be then incorporated to the user's projects.",
    "A step-by-step guide for extending the prototype to support prompt and code generation for further AI systems, beyond the ones already implemented, is detailed in the repository [62].We elaborate the aforementioned capabilities in the following subsections.",
    "Prompt customizationPlatform-independent prompts facilitate prompt migration: changing the generative AI system that is consuming prompts.",
    "In order to illustrate the capabilities of the Impromptuframework, we have implemented generators that transform the platformindependent prompt into the specific prompt for OpenAI's text-to-text ChatGPT, and for two particular text-to-image generative AI systems: Midjourney [64] and Stable Diffusion (SD).",
    "In particular, we are targeting the AUTOMATIC1111 webui for Stable Diffusion [65].The transformation of a prompt defined with Impromptuto a valid input for ChatGPT is quite straightforward."
  ],
